  "industry_note": "UNS C17200 / EN CW101C / CuBe2 / Alloy 25 / DIN 2.1247 — precipitation-hardenable Cu-Be alloy (Cu bal, Be 1.8-2.0, Ni+Co 0.20-0.6). 가장 strong copper alloy. TF00 (peak TH04 (CW 37% + IACS 22-25% (steel 보다 5× conductive). Non-sparking — petrochemical / 위험 환경 hand tool, mold pin, electrical contact spring, oil/gas drilling. ⚠ Be dust inhalation 강한 발암성 (NIOSH carcinogen, OSHA PEL 0.2 μg/m³).",
